{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-08",
 "title": "Reminding Diggs About the Moff",
 "summary": "In a corridor of the NRSC Deliverance, the New Republic Intelligence captain Jonau Diggs crosses paths with Luke Skywalker while wandering with his datapad. Luke asks whether there is any progress on the Death Star, and Diggs admits there is nothing new beyond reconfirming its location and chasing unverified rumors. The conversation turns to the dangerous Sith Moff Morganna Tazecks, who slipped out of Caspian custody while Intelligence was preoccupied; Luke, recalling his own hard lessons about her, asks Diggs to look into her whereabouts. Diggs agrees to assign agents to the matter as a welcome change of pace, and the two part cordially with promises to keep each other informed.",
